<template>
  <v-dialog
      :value="isOpened"
      max-width="290"
      class="justify-center"
      persistent
  >
    <v-card>
      <v-card-title class="text-h5">
        Use Google's location service?
      </v-card-title>

      <v-card-text>
        Let Google help apps determine location. This means sending anonymous location data to Google, even when no
        apps are running.
      </v-card-text>

      <v-card-actions>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>

        <v-btn
            color="green darken-1"
            text
            @click="$emit('close', false)"
        >
          Disagree
        </v-btn>

        <v-btn
            color="green darken-1"
            text
            @click="$emit('close', false)"
        >
          Agree
        </v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
  </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'LoginDialog',
  props: {
    isOpened: Boolean
  },
  data() {
    return {
    }
  },
}
</script>
